%^BOLD%^-=%^BOLD%^%^RED%^Freedom Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

You are a spirit of freedom and a staunch foe against all who would enslave and oppress.

Clerics with the Freedom Domain gain the following benefits:
-- Greater resistance to paralysis effects

The freedom domain contains the following spells:

haste, gaseous form, flee the scene, greater teleport, freedom

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Velik, Callamir

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^